{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_34","type":"agent_message","text":"Plan for the implementation:\n1. Add a library integration layer that resolves either a canonical stimulus bundle or a scene description into one normalized retinal-recording request.\n2. Extend the public retinal visual-source API just enough to carry stable source IDs and hashes, so pose-aware playback caches do not collide.\n3. Add a thin CLI for `record` and `replay`, then cover it with fixture-style tests for one stimulus path and one scene path.\n4. Document the local command workflow and finish with repo tests, a targeted smoke run, staging, and a non-amended commit."}}
